            <p class="title">
              Impromptu Jam Session at the Firehouse
            </p>
            <p class="photographer">
              David Tribby
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
               <!--Description-->
            </p>
            <p class="description-copy">
              My close friend is an aspiring musician. One day, he was walking to a performance. Passing a firehouse, one of the firemen noticed Matt’s guitar and struck up a conversation. A couple minutes later he was free-styling guitar for a couple guys sitting in front of the fire truck. To get this shot, I only used natural light. 
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
              camera
            </p>
            <p class="camera-copy">
              Canon EOS Rebel T2i DSLR
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
