      <div class="description">
            <br/>
            <p class="title">
              When a dream becomes a photograph
            </p>
            <p class="photographer">
              Celso Pereira Jr.
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
               <!--Description-->
            </p>
            <p class="description-copy">
              I waited for the sun to set just enough where I could still get ambient light to illuminate the subject, but not from an obvious light source or direction. I pushed the limits of the camera sensor and lens aperture to give me depth of field without sacrificing shadow details, which were important for the feeling of "wondering into dreamland."
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
              camera
            </p>
            <p class="camera-copy">
              Canon EOS 5D Mark II DSLR
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
