            <br/>
            <p class="title">
              NO FEAR!
            </p>
            <p class="photographer">
              Lynne Gilbert
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
               <!--Description-->
            </p>
            <p class="description-copy">
              When shooting waves, I always use the sports/action mode. It’s a phenomenal tool that I feel a lot of people don’t utilize nearly enough to get quick action shots. It was peak high tide and the waves were pounding and coming in hard. I captured a great series with the sports setting. Had I not used it I don’t think I would have captured half of the images I did, including this one.
            </p>


            <p class="sub-heads">
              camera
            </p>
            <p class="camera-copy">
              Canon EOS 60D DSLR
